NOTE ON DATA AND THIRD-PARTY MATERIALS

This license covers the source code, notebooks, and documentation in this
repository ONLY. It does NOT cover the underlying datasets, which are not
redistributed here (see .gitignore) and remain subject to their own terms:

  * Agricultural Climate Data Collection (ACDC) — climate, soil, and yield
    panels (Schlenker & Roberts, 2009, PNAS). Obtain from the original source.
  * USDA ERS, Commodity Costs and Returns — crop prices and operating costs.
    https://www.ers.usda.gov/data-products/commodity-costs-and-returns

Users must obtain these datasets independently and comply with their
respective licenses and terms of use.
